docs.text: Documentation : View it on website Source Code : View it on Github FastAPI X is a CLI tool to manage your FastAPI projects. Features 🚀 ¶ Generate a new FastAPI project Generate components to your project Installation ✍️ ¶ FastAPI X can be installed by running pip install fastapix . Usage 📖 ¶ FastAPI X is a CLI tool, so you can run it by typing fastapix in your terminal.
